● Based on what's already built, here are features you can add:
                                                                                                                                        
  ---
For Members                                                                                                                             - Push notifications — fee due reminders, attendance streaks                                                                        
  - Workout/exercise log — let members track their workouts                                                                               - Body measurements tracker — weight, BMI over time with a chart                                                                    
  - Diet/nutrition tips section — static or dynamic content
  - Member profile photo upload
  - Referral system — member refers a friend, gets a discount



  ---
  For Owner
  - SMS/WhatsApp notifications to members for fee reminders
  - Expense tracking — gym expenses (electricity, equipment, rent)
  - Equipment inventory management
  - Multi-branch support — owner manages more than one gym location
  - Revenue vs expense comparison charts
  - Member retention reports — who's about to lapse
  - Announcement/notice board — broadcast messages to all members
  - Discount/promo codes for membership fees
  - Trial membership support — free X-day trial period

  ---
  General / Platform
  - Dark/light theme toggle
  - In-app chat between staff and members
  - Document upload — contracts, medical certificates
  - Backup & export — export member data to Excel/CSV
  - Member birthday reminders for the owner/staff
  - Feedback/rating system — members rate the gym

  ---
  The biggest value-adds for a real gym business would be expense tracking, SMS/WhatsApp fee reminders, and multi-branch support.
